
START HERE
==========

Read this file first!



SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-------------------

You will need
 * A 64-bit Intel or AMD machine
 * Ubuntu 14.10 or better


SETUP
-----

To set up the project (you only need to do this once):

1. Install git, DTS tools and GCC for native & target architectures

    sudo apt-get install git gcc device-tree-compiler bc build-essential gcc-arm-none-eabi

2. If you want, you can also install these optional packages

    sudo apt-get install cscope
    sudo apt-get install gitk

3. If you are using Imperas OVP for simulation, you should install that separately.


4. Run setup:
    make setup

